<h5 id="subject_764606">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=80919.msg764606#msg764606" rel="nofollow">【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.88 --100</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_764606'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_764606'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2015-11-18, 周三 00:20:15 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_764606_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
