<div class="inner" id="msg_765028"><strong>范例</strong><br><strong>选择技能</strong><br><strong>James</strong><br>　　James为他的人物技能选择了优先级E，这给了他18点技能点以供分配。在这个优先级上，James不会获得任何技能组点数。多亏他之前在魔法和共鸣竖列选择了横排B，他已经拥有了两个技能：编码4级和注册4级。查看技能列表，James认为以下行动技能的等级分配会有所帮助：自动化2级、电脑3级、电子战1级、伪造2级、骇入5级、硬件1级、察觉2级、手枪2级。<br>　　对于知识和语言技能，James获得16点免费点数【（直觉4+逻辑4）×2=16】。James选择了英语作为母语，然后让他的人物从街头学了一点儿日语。他购买的知识节能包括BTL贩子、公司、掮客、本地碟客、本地技术巫师、矩阵安全措施、约翰逊先生、新无政府主义以及操作系统。James基于他可用点数为这些技能分配了等级。James的人物在这一步看起来是这样的：<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">EXAMPLE<br>CHOOSING SKILLS<br>JAMES<br>&nbsp; James selects Priority Level E for his character’s skills, giving him 18 skill points to assign. At this level, James does not receive any Skill Group points. Thanks to his earlier choice of Row B in the Magic and Resonance column, he already has two skills: Compiling 4 and Registering 4. Looking over the skills list, James decides the following Active Skills would be useful at the listed ranks: Automatics 2, Computer 3, Electronic Warfare 1, Forgery 2, Hacking 5, Hardware 1, Perception 2, Pistols 2.<br>&nbsp; For Knowledge and Language skills, James receives16 free points [(Intuition 4 + Logic 4) x 2 = 16]. James selects English for his Native language, and decides that his character has picked up a little Japanese from the streets. He purchases Knowledge Skills covering BTL Dealers, Corporations, Fixers, Local Deckers, Local Technomancers, Matrix Security Measures, Mr. Johnsons, Neo-Anarchists, and Operating Systems. James assigns ratings to these skills based on the points he has available. This is how James’ character looks at this point:</div></div></div><br><strong>Rob</strong><br>　　Rob，巨魔街头武士，为他的人物技能选择了优先级C。这给了他28点技能点和2点技能组点数。Rob把两点技能组点数都投在了运动技能组上。因为他的人物是战斗型，Rob选择购买了自动化5级、利刃4级、电脑1级、急救2级、重武器1级、长管枪3级、察觉1级、驾驶地面器械2级、手枪2级、投掷武器2级以及徒手格斗5级。<br>　　基于他的直觉和逻辑属性等级，Rob得到12点免费点数购买知识和语言技能。对于他的知识技能，Rob选取了Bismarck城市知识、加美联邦军事条例、加美联邦知识、掮客和狂奔者藏身处。<br>　　Rob设定当他在加美联邦军队时驻扎在加美联邦和苏国边境上。在那里，他学了点儿达科塔语以及苏国知识。Rob人物的母语是英语。<br>　　根据他的人物范型分配完他的技能点后，Rob的技能看起起来是这样的：<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">ROB<br>&nbsp; Rob the troll street samurai has chosen to use Priority Level C for his character’s skills. This gives him 28 skill points and 2 skill group points. Rob chooses the Athletics skill group for both his skill group points. Because his character is combat-orientated, Rob chooses buy Automatics 5, Blades 4, Computer 1, First Aid 2, Heavy Weapons 1, Longarms 3, Perception 1, Pilot Ground Craft 2, Pistols 2, Throwing Weapons 2, and Unarmed Combat 5.<br>&nbsp; Based on his Intuition and Logic Attribute ratings, Rob gets 12 free points to buy Knowledge and Language skills. For his Knowledge skills, Rob takes Bismarck City Knowledge, UCAS Military Regulations, UCAS Knowledge, Fixers, and Runner Hangouts. <br>&nbsp; Rob decides that his character was stationed near the UCAS/Sioux border when in the UCAS military. While there, he picked up a little Dakota, as well as knowledge on the Sioux Nation. Rob’s character’s native language is English.<br>&nbsp; After massaging his skill points to fit his concept, Rob’s skills look like this:</div></div></div><br><strong>Kyra</strong><br>　　Kyra准备代替小组出面人的位置，所以她需要混合战斗技能和社交技能。因为她为魔法和共鸣竖列选择了横排A，她已经拥有了法术施放5级以及法术反制5级。她为她的技能选择横排C。如同Rob，Kyra获得28点技能点和2点技能组点数。Kyra决定将她的技能组点数花在咒法技能组上。然后她为她的人物选择了如下技能：星界感知3级、自动化4级、电脑1级、欺诈4级、礼仪2级、锁匠2级、谈判4级、察觉3级、驾驶地面器械2级以及手枪3级。现在选完她的技能之后，她可以回头决定哪些要用她的异能来增强。她为提升精度【技能】选择了自动化技能，为提高能力【技能】选择了手枪。<br>　　基于她的人物直觉和逻辑值，Kyra的人物获得14点用于知识和语言的点数【（4+3）×2=14】。她选择获得如下技能：掮客1级、执法策略2级、有组织犯罪1级、街头毒品贩子2级、街头帮派识别3级、街头帮派政治3级、Kyra的人物将英语作为母语，但同时也会点儿赛普瑞希尔语，在Tír Tairngire和Tír na nÓg常见的精灵语言。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">KYRA<br>&nbsp; Kyra intends to be the face of the group, so she will need to have a mix of combat skills and social skills. Since she chose Row A for her Magic or Resonance column, she already has the Spellcasting and Counterspelling skills at 5. She selects Priority Row C for her skills. Like Rob, Kyra receives 28 skill points and 2 skill group points. Kyra decides to spend her skill group points on the Conjuring skill group. Then she chooses the following skills for her character: Assensing 3, Automatics 4, Computers 1, Con 4, Etiquette 2, Locksmith 2, Negotiation 4, Perception 3, Pilot Ground Craft 2, and Pistols 3. Now that she has selected her skills, she can go back and decide which ones will be augmented by her adept powers. For her Enhanced Accuracy [Skill], she chooses her Automatics skill, and for her Improved Ability [Skill] she chooses Pistols.<br>&nbsp; Based on her character’s Intuition and Logic scores, Kyra’s character receives 14 skill points for knowledge and language skills [(4 + 3) x 2 = 14]. She chooses to acquire the following skills: Fixers 1, Law Enforcement Tactics 2, Organized Crime 1, Street Drug Dealers 2, Street Gang Identifcation 3, and Street Gang Politics 3. Kyra’s character has English as her native language, but she also knows a little Sperethiel, a prominent elven language found in Tír Tairngire and Tír na nÓg. </div></div></div></div>
