<h5 id="subject_765514">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=80919.msg765514#msg765514" rel="nofollow">Re: 【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.88 --</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_765514'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_765514'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #4 于:</strong> 2015-11-23, 周一 23:51:02 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_765514_quick_mod"></div>
