<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_765514"><span style="font-size: 24pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>第七步：</strong></span><br><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>使用你的剩余业力</strong></span><br>　　这一步是玩家在最后结算前最后一次打磨她的人物的机会。此时关于她的人物的背景故事以及她想让她的人物看起来像什么样子，玩家应该已经有了一个很不错的主意。现在所有剩余的业力都可以用来打磨人物，选取或提升技能、购买额外法术、获得绑定精魂、在游戏开始时使用的粘合法器、购买人脉等等。参见“额外购买和限制表”，注意所有用业力购买项目的限制。如果玩家希望保留一些业力在之后的游戏中使用，她可以这样做，但最多携带7业力。当提升技能和属性时，要留意人物创建的多种限制：只有一个属性可以达到天生属性上限、装备限制设备等级少于等于6或可用等级少于等于12。在购买业力时，这些规则依然适用。<br>　　当为属性或技能使用业力时，参见“人物发展”章节提升人物的规则（P.103）。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Step Seven:<br>Spending Your Leftover Karma<br>This step is the player’s last opportunity to polish her character before making the final calculations. By this time the player should have a pretty good idea of her character’s backstory and what she wants her character to look like. Any remaining Karma can now be invested in smoothing out any rough edges, picking up or improving skills, buying additional spells, acquiring bound spirits, bonding foci to be used at the start of the game, purchasing contacts, etc. Refer to the Additional Purchases and Restrictions table to note any special restrictions on purchasing items with Karma. If a player wishes to keep some Karma for use later in the game, she may do so, though the maximum carryover is 7 Karma. When raising skills and attributes, keep in mind the various restrictions of character creation:Only one attribute can be at the natural attribute limit, and gear is restricted to items with Device Ratings of 6 or less or an Availability of 12 or less. These rules still apply to when you are spending Karma.<br>&nbsp; When spending Karma for attributes or skills, refer to the rules for improving the character in the Character Advancement section (p. 103).</div></div></div><br><strong>人脉</strong><br>　　人脉是暗影狂奔者生活中的一个重要部分。人脉会贩卖非法或很难弄到的物品，为狂奔者提供潜在的工作机会，知道狂奔者们想要知道的东西得从哪里入手，在一家严密守卫的公司的布局上知识渊博。有些人脉也可以提供狂奔者成瘾的物质、为偷来的东西销赃，甚至如果他们足够忠诚，还会把暗影狂奔者从孤星的牢房里保释出来。有各种各样的人脉可以投资。每个人物都会获得免费业力花费在初始的人脉上。这个业力的数量等于人物魅力等级×3。<br>　　每个人脉都有一个联系和忠诚等级。玩家购买的任何人脉都必须在联系和忠诚上至少有1级。联系代表一个人脉的范围和影响，从暗影之中到大千世界，让一件事情结束或让一件事情发生。忠诚反映了人脉有多忠于狂奔者以及没有武力和钱财的情况下会忍受狂奔者多久。忠诚1或2，人脉和人物只是生意关系。狂奔者不在时，他们会不安，但只是因为与之相关的利润损失，而不是因为任何亲密的个人感情。更高的忠诚等级，人脉和人物的关系更强大也更私人（如友情），更可能冒着风险或抛下自己的事来帮助人物。有关人脉的使用规则，见P.386。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Contacts<br>Contacts are a vital part of a shadowrunner’s life. Contacts sell illegal or hard-to-obtain items, alert runners to potential employment, know someone who knows someone who knows something the runner wants to know, or are knowledgeable about the layout of a heavily guarded corporate compound. Some contacts can supply substances runners are addicted too, fence stolen goods, and maybe, if they’re loyal enough, bail the shadowrunner out of the Lone Star holding cell. Having a wide variety of Contacts can be a valuable investment. Every character receives free Karma to spend on their initial contacts. This Karma is equal to a Character’s Charisma rating x 3.<br>&nbsp; Each Contact has a Connection and a Loyalty rating. Any Contacts a player buys must have a minimum rating of 1 in Connection and a minimum rating of 1 in Loyalty. Connection represents how much reach and influence a Contact has, both within the shadows and in the world at large, to get things done or to make things happen. Loyalty reflects how loyal the contact is to the runner and how much they’ll endure without shattering whatever bond the two have. At Loyalty 1 or 2, the Contact has only a business relationship with the character. Any qualms they have about turning the runner in are tied to profits they may lose if the runner isn’t around, not so much because of any close personal feelings. With a higher Loyalty rating, the Contact has a stronger and more personal relationship (i.e., friendship) with the character, and is more likely to take some risk or go out of his way to help the character. For specific rules on the use of Contacts, see p. 386.</div></div></div><br><strong>范例人脉</strong><br>武器贩子、走私者、帮派成员、公司社畜、掮客、塔利斯贩子（魔法物品卖家）、受贿黑警、机师、机械师、街头医生<br><br><strong><strong>额外购买和限制表</strong></strong><br>项目　　　　业力花费（人物创建时）　　　　　　　　　　　　　限制<br>绑定精魂　　每个服务１业力（精魂法强等于人物魔法等级）　　　绑定精魂数量最多等于魅力属性<br>复杂形式　　每个复杂形式４业力　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　人物创建时，复杂形式最多等于逻辑属性<br>法术　　　　每个法术５业力　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　人物创建时，人物知道的法术、仪式、试剂最多等于魔法等级×２<br>粘合法器　　多样，见P.318粘合法器花费　　　　　　　　　　　人物创建时，所有可以粘合法器的总法强最多等于魔法等级×２<br>人脉　　　　每级联系１业力，每级忠诚１业力（至少需要２业力）人物创建时，一个人脉的花费不能超过７业力。人脉数量没有限制<br>注册幽魂　　每个１业力（幽魂等级等于人物共鸣等级）　　　　　注册幽魂数量最多等于魅力属性<br><br><br><br>接下来的范例实在是没什么可译的，就是剩下的业力换来了人脉和技能。</div>
</div>
</div>
